{"tid":1315214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 退或留］ 沙田友畀意見","createTime":"2019-07-14T13:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T14:04:38.000Z","uid":266643,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"898a84d91cb2db036337e83bfcb50afdc90ba2e1","tid":1315214,"uid":266643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjAAy9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjAAy9a.jpg&h=a08d6807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ap2rFPb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAp2rFPb.jpg&h=1e980c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實沙田十字路口 係一個死胡同<br />\n出路嘅應該淨返 沙田站<br />\n但係地鐵站多數都有警察<br />\n所以其實都只不過係困獸鬥<br />\n<br />\n警察嘅支援點都大過留守嘅人<br />\n<br />\n留守嘅我支持同埋尊重,,<br />\n但要走嘅 都真係考慮下.. <br />\n<br />\nBe Water!"},{"pid":"533377450d8760ade1e0e36016864f79d341f74a","tid":1315214,"uid":84771,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"退，根本冇嘢好守，留翻有用之軀等21號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18102099ab6f6fcdfa53ce386631e7506db19ac2","tid":1315214,"uid":266643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"a2d646772e73b7743a5040eb05f77f86f27b55ef","tid":1315214,"uid":266643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4442543935618b4930b88a45e489d24fb6e01042","tid":1315214,"uid":203057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"退啦 個地理環境根本守唔到 而家俾人圍撚死晒"},{"pid":"1f615b5f0a28db6a95c5fd78e6d411547650a03f","tid":1315214,"uid":266643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:13:06.000Z","msg":"走啦咁多位, 留返下次21"},{"pid":"df727cc26b93d44960700e65f69b8d